<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: { sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'] },
                    colors: {
                        brand: { 50: '#fff0f0', 100: '#fecaca', 200: '#fca5a5', 500: '#dc2626', 600: '#b91c1c', 700: '#991b1b', 800: '#7f1d1d' },
                        danger: { 500: '#dc2626', 600: '#b91c1c' }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        /* CSS tùy chỉnh nhỏ cho thanh cuộn và hiệu ứng mượt */
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .line-clamp-2 {
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hide-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen text-slate-800">

    <%- include('navbar') %>

        <main class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-8 mb-12">
            <div class="relative w-full h-[450px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl group">
                <img src="/images/banner-trangchu.jpg"
                    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
                    alt="Banner TV">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/80 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-center px-12 md:px-20">
                    <span class="text-red-400 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Đón Lễ Lớn</span>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Sale Chạm Đáy
                        50%<br>Smart Tivi 4K</h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-200 mb-8 max-w-lg">Nâng cấp không gian giải trí tại gia với các siêu
                        phẩm OLED, Neo QLED thế hệ mới nhất. Miễn phí lắp đặt.</p>
                    <a href="/sanpham"
                        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-700 to-brand-600 hover:from-brand-800 hover:to-brand-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full w-fit shadow-lg shadow-brand-600/30 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
                        <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge-fill mr-2"></i> Khám Phá Ngay
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative -mt-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl z-10">
                <form action="/sanpham" method="GET"
                    class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 p-2 rounded-full shadow-xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="flex-1 flex items-center pl-4 w-full">
                        <i class="bi bi-search text-slate-400 text-xl"></i>
                        <input type="text" name="timkiem" placeholder="Nhập tên Tivi cần tìm..."
                            value="<%= query.timkiem || '' %>"
                            class="w-full bg-transparent border-none focus:ring-0 text-slate-700 px-4 py-3 outline-none placeholder-slate-400">
                    </div>
                    <div class="h-10 w-px bg-slate-200 hidden md:block"></div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-auto px-4">
                        <select name="gia"
                            class="w-full bg-transparent border-none focus:ring-0 text-slate-600 font-medium outline-none cursor-pointer">
                            <option value="">Tất cả mức giá</option>
                            <option value="duoi10">Dưới 10 Triệu</option>
                            <option value="10den20">10 - 20 Triệu</option>
                            <option value="tren20">Trên 20 Triệu</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit"
                        class="w-full md:w-auto bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-colors">
                        Tìm Kiếm
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </main>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex-grow mb-16">

            <% if(spgiamgia.length> 0) { %>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900"><i
                                class="bi bi-lightning-charge-fill text-red-500 mr-2"></i>Flash Sale Giờ Vàng</h2>
                        <% if (!isFlashSaleReal) { %>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">Sản phẩm đang bán chạy — <a href="/sanpham"
                                    class="text-brand-600 font-semibold hover:underline">Xem thêm &rarr;</a></p>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">Giảm giá thật trong hôm nay — <a href="/sanpham"
                                        class="text-brand-600 font-semibold hover:underline">Xem thêm &rarr;</a></p>
                                <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <% if (isFlashSaleReal) { %>
                        <div
                            class="hidden sm:flex items-center bg-red-50 border border-red-100 text-red-600 font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                            <i class="bi bi-clock-fill mr-2"></i> Hôm nay
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
                    <% spgiamgia.forEach(sp=> { %>
                        <% let phanTramGiam=(isFlashSaleReal && sp.GiaGoc> 0) ? Math.round((1 - sp.GiaBan / sp.GiaGoc) *
                            100) : 0;
                            %>
                            <div
                                class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300 relative flex flex-col group">

                                <% if (isFlashSaleReal && phanTramGiam> 0) { %>
                                    <span
                                        class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-red-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-lg z-10">-
                                        <%= phanTramGiam %>%</span>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <span
                                            class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-brand-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-lg z-10"><i
                                                class="bi bi-fire"></i> Bán chạy</span>
                                        <% } %>

                                            <a href="/sanpham/<%= sp._id %>" class="flex flex-col flex-grow">
                                                <div
                                                    class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-4">
                                                    <img src="/images/<%= sp.HinhAnh %>"
                                                        class="max-h-full object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                                                        alt="<%= sp.TenSP %>">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="flex flex-col flex-grow">
                                                    <span
                                                        class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-600 bg-brand-50 px-2 py-1 rounded-md w-fit mb-2">
                                                        <%= sp.HangSanXuat ? sp.HangSanXuat.TenHang : 'Chính Hãng' %>
                                                    </span>
                                                    <h6
                                                        class="text-slate-800 font-bold leading-tight mb-2 line-clamp-2 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">
                                                        <%= sp.TenSP %>
                                                    </h6>

                                                    <% let tbSaoKM=0; let soDGKM=0; if(sp.DanhGia && sp.DanhGia.length>
                                                        0) {
                                                        soDGKM = sp.DanhGia.length;
                                                        tbSaoKM = (sp.DanhGia.reduce((sum, dg) => sum + dg.SoSao, 0) /
                                                        soDGKM).toFixed(1);
                                                        } %>
                                                        <div class="flex items-center text-sm mb-4">
                                                            <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-amber-400 mr-1"></i>
                                                            <span class="font-bold text-slate-700">
                                                                <%= tbSaoKM> 0 ? tbSaoKM : 'Chưa có' %>
                                                            </span>
                                                            <% if(soDGKM> 0) { %><span class="text-slate-400 ml-1">(<%=
                                                                        soDGKM %>)</span>
                                                                <% } %>
                                                        </div>

                                                        <div class="mt-auto">
                                                            <% if (isFlashSaleReal && sp.GiaGoc> 0) { %>
                                                                <div class="text-slate-400 line-through text-sm">
                                                                    <%= sp.GiaGoc.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %> đ
                                                                </div>
                                                                <% } %>
                                                                    <div
                                                                        class="<%= isFlashSaleReal ? 'text-red-500' : 'text-brand-600' %> font-extrabold text-xl">
                                                                        <%= sp.GiaBan.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %> đ
                                                                    </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </a>
                                            <a href="/themvaogio/<%= sp._id %>"
                                                class="mt-4 bg-red-50 hover:bg-red-500 text-red-600 hover:text-white border border-red-200 hover:border-red-500 font-bold w-full py-2.5 rounded-xl text-center transition-colors">
                                                <i class="bi bi-cart-plus mr-1"></i> Chọn Mua
                                            </a>
                            </div>
                            <% }) %>
                </div>
                <% } %>



                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6 mt-12 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900"><i
                                class="bi bi-grid-fill text-brand-500 mr-2"></i>Sản Phẩm Nổi Bật</h3>
                        <a href="/sanpham"
                            class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-800 font-semibold flex items-center group">
                            Xem tất cả <i
                                class="bi bi-arrow-right ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8">
                        <% if(sanpham.length> 0) { %>
                            <% sanpham.slice(0, 8).forEach(sp=> { %>
                                <div
                                    class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group">
                                    <a href="/sanpham/<%= sp._id %>" class="flex flex-col flex-grow">
                                        <div
                                            class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-4">
                                            <img src="/images/<%= sp.HinhAnh %>"
                                                class="max-h-full object-contain group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                                                alt="<%= sp.TenSP %>">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="flex flex-col flex-grow">
                                            <span
                                                class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 rounded-md w-fit mb-2">
                                                <%= sp.HangSanXuat ? sp.HangSanXuat.TenHang : 'Chính Hãng' %>
                                            </span>
                                            <h6
                                                class="text-slate-800 font-bold leading-tight mb-2 line-clamp-2 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">
                                                <%= sp.TenSP %>
                                            </h6>

                                            <% let tbSao=0; let soDanhGia=0; if(sp.DanhGia && sp.DanhGia.length> 0) {
                                                soDanhGia = sp.DanhGia.length;
                                                tbSao = (sp.DanhGia.reduce((sum, dg) => sum + dg.SoSao, 0) /
                                                soDanhGia).toFixed(1);
                                                }
                                                %>
                                                <div class="flex items-center text-sm mb-4">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-amber-400 mr-1"></i>
                                                    <span class="font-bold text-slate-700">
                                                        <%= tbSao> 0 ? tbSao : 'Chưa có' %>
                                                    </span>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="mt-auto text-brand-600 font-extrabold text-xl">
                                                    <%= sp.GiaBan.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %> đ
                                                </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="/themvaogio/<%= sp._id %>"
                                        class="mt-4 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-brand-50 text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-600 border border-slate-200 hover:border-brand-300 font-bold w-full py-2.5 rounded-xl text-center transition-colors">
                                        <i class="bi bi-cart-plus mr-1"></i> Chọn Mua
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                                <% }) %>
                                    <% } %>
                    </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white py-16 mt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900"><i
                            class="bi bi-newspaper text-brand-500 mr-2"></i>Góc Công Nghệ</h3>
                    <a href="/tintuc"
                        class="bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-brand-500 hover:text-brand-600 text-slate-600 rounded-full px-6 py-2 font-semibold transition-colors">
                        Xem tất cả
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <% if (tintuc && tintuc.length> 0) { %>
                        <% tintuc.forEach(t=> { %>
                            <div class="group cursor-pointer">
                                <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl mb-4 h-56 shadow-sm">
                                    <% let imgSrc=t.HinhAnh.startsWith('http') ? t.HinhAnh : '/images/' + t.HinhAnh; %>
                                        <img src="<%= imgSrc %>"
                                            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
                                            alt="<%= t.TieuDe %>">
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2 font-medium">
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar3 mr-2"></i>
                                    <%= new Date(t.NgayDang).toLocaleDateString('vi-VN') %>
                                </div>
                                <h5
                                    class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">
                                    <%= t.TieuDe %>
                                </h5>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 line-clamp-2 text-sm">
                                    <%= t.TomTat %>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <% }) %>
                                <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
                <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6"><i
                            class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-danger-500 mr-2"></i>Hệ Thống Showroom</h4>
                    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-inner h-[350px]">
                        <iframe
                            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d490.6158388358315!2d105.45986987650394!3d10.347745325088344!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x310a73994fe3fd7f%3A0x5e333044c1f1b7c0!2zUXXDoW4gVHLDoCBT4buvYSBUaMO5eSBUcmFuZw!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1774806226593!5m2!1svi!2s"
                            width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6"><i
                            class="bi bi-facebook text-brand-600 mr-2"></i>Fanpage TVN</h4>
                    <div
                        class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-inner bg-slate-50 h-[350px] flex items-center justify-center">
                        <iframe
                            src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/page.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnghi.vinh.58726%2F&tabs=timeline&width=400&height=350&small_header=false&adapt_container_width=true&hide_cover=false&show_facepile=true&appId"
                            width="100%" height="100%" style="border:none; overflow:hidden;" scrolling="no"
                            frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true"
                            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share"></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-16 mt-8" id="lien-he">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div
                    class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-8 md:p-10 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-600 mb-8"><i class="bi bi-shop mr-2"></i>Cửa Hàng Tivi TVN
                    </h4>

                    <div class="flex items-start mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-slate-100">
                        <div
                            class="bg-red-50 text-danger-500 w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">Trụ sở chính:</p>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">54/98 Đường Trần Quang Khải, Phường Mỹ Thới, TP.
                                Long Xuyên, An Giang</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-slate-100">
                        <div
                            class="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-500 w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <i class="bi bi-telephone-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">Hotline Tư Vấn:</p>
                            <a href="tel:0931082845"
                                class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">0931.082.845</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="bg-amber-50 text-amber-500 w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <i class="bi bi-envelope-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">Email Hỗ Trợ:</p>
                            <a href="mailto:hotro@tivin.com"
                                class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">hotro@tivin.com</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-brand-700 to-brand-800 rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full -mr-20 -mt-20 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700">
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-40 h-40 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full -ml-10 -mb-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700">
                    </div>

                    <i
                        class="bi bi-headset text-7xl mb-6 opacity-90 z-10 drop-shadow-md group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4 z-10">Hỗ Trợ Khách Hàng 24/7</h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-100 text-lg mb-8 max-w-md z-10">Bạn cần tư vấn cấu hình Tivi hoặc làm thủ tục
                        trả góp 0%? Đừng ngần ngại gọi ngay cho chuyên viên của chúng tôi!</p>
                    <a href="tel:0931082845"
                        class="bg-white text-brand-700 hover:bg-brand-50 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 z-10 flex items-center">
                        <i class="bi bi-telephone-outbound-fill mr-2"></i> GỌI TỔNG ĐÀI TVN
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('footer') %>

            <a href="https://zalo.me/0931082845" target="_blank"
                class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-700 text-white p-4 rounded-full shadow-2xl hover:shadow-brand-600/50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 z-50 group"
                title="Chat Zalo">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor"
                    class="w-8 h-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path
                        d="M8 15c4.418 0 8-3.134 8-7s-3.582-7-8-7-8 3.134-8 7c0 1.76.743 3.37 1.97 4.6-.097 1.016-.417 2.13-.771 2.966-.079.186.074.394.273.362 2.256-.37 3.597-.938 4.18-1.234A9.06 9.06 0 0 0 8 15z" />
                </svg>
            </a>

            <script>
                document.addEventListener('keydown', function (event) {
                    if (event.ctrlKey && event.shiftKey && (event.key === 'b' || event.key === 'B')) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        window.location.href = '/admin/dangnhap';
                    }
                });
            </script>
</body>

</html>